description: The MSCI USA Industrials Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large and mid cap US companies which are part of the Industrials sector as classified by the Global Industry Classification Standard (GICS) Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Reviewed on a quarterly basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.msci.com
name: Xtrackers MSCI USA Industrials UCITS ETF 1D
